{
  "texts": [
    "E-Mate was a virtual agent incorporating visualization that provided initial feedback on the assessment.",
    "Automated evaluation of review helpfulness was investigated by Liu et al. (2023), with the help of deep learning models and natural language processing techniques.",
    "The study evaluated the performance of self-training in predicting the helpfulness of peer reviews.",
    "Also, an advanced self-training framework was proposed by tailoring knowledge distillation and noise injection to further improve model performance.",
    "Two papers concerned the quality of elaborated feedback."
  ]
}